<h2><strong><span style="background-color: #ffcc00;">Spain Travel Destinations</span></strong></h2>
<p>Spain is one of the most visited countries in the world, it attracts millions of tourists every year because of its amazing cities rich in culture, amazing food and beaches.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Take a look at the list of the most visited countries in 2019 (Before the pandemic)</p>
<p>10. England (36.9 million tourists)<br />9. Germany (39.4 million tourists)<br />8. Thailand (39.7 million tourists)<br />7. Mexico (44.9 million tourists)<br />6. Turkey (52.5 million tourists)<br />5. Italy (64.6 million tourists)<br />4. China (67.5 million tourists)<br />3. United States of America (78.7 million tourists)<br />2. Spain (83.8 million tourists)<br />1. France (90.3 million tourists)</p>
