<h4></h4>
<p>Quite impressive right? Now let's have a look at some of the best cities to visit in Spain:</p>
<h4>Madrid</h4>
<p><img src="https://youropize.net/en/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Madrid-en-un-Dia-Circulo-de-Bellas-Artes-1.jpg" alt="Trulli" width="507" height="338" /></p>
<p><span style="font-style: italic;">- Capital of Spain, rich in art and culture. Madrid is perfect for those who love history and art whilst still experiencing the busy and modern city life.</span></p>
